title: 178 - The Rat Takeover
description: Today’s episode kicks off with the Covid Cowboy himself Tone Digs leading the way. The boys give their condolences out to our man Jay who is getting married this weekend. The boys jump right into the Pod FOD, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Today’s Fod includes some pretty impressive rats, some out of pocket “linked-in” comments and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
